#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.min"
msgstr "# triton.language.min"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:4
msgid "简介：在指定维度上返回最小值"
msgstr "Introduction: Returns the minimum value on the specified dimension."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.min(input, axis=None, return_indices=False, return_indices_tie_break_left=True, keep_dims=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | 输入的张量数据 |\n"
"| `axis`   | `int` | 指定在哪个维度上进行规约 |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | 如果为True，保留被规约的维度(大小为1) |\n"
"| `return_indices` | `bool` | True返回最小值的同时返回最小值相关所在下标 |\n"
"| `return_indices_tie_break_left` | `bool` | True如果多个元素有相同的最小值，返回最左侧最小值的下标。|\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | --- |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | The input tensor data |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | Specifies the dimension along which to reduce |\n"
"| `keep_dims` | `bool` | If True, retains the reduced dimension (size 1) |\n"
"| `return_indices` | `bool` | If True, returns the indices of the minimum values |\n"
"| `return_indices_tie_break_left` | `bool` | If True and multiple elements have the same minimum value, returns the index of the leftmost minimum value. |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：同`input`的shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: A tensor with the same shape as `input`.\n"

