#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:32
msgid "### 2.3 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.3 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:34
msgid "更多示例参考triton-ascend代码仓，ascend/examples/generalization_cases/test_min.py"
msgstr "For more examples, refer to the triton-ascend code repository, ascend/examples/generalization_cases/test_min.py"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Reduction_Ops/min.md:36
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_min_1d(in_ptr0, out_ptr1, xnumel, XBLOCK : tl.constexpr):\n"
"    xoffset = tl.program_id(0) + tl.arange(0, XBLOCK)\n"
"    tmp0 = tl.load(in_ptr0 + xoffset, None)\n"
"    tmp4 = tl.min(tmp0, 0)\n"
"    tl.store(out_ptr1, tmp4, None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

